__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.DS_Store
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.venv/
# Runtime scratch (digital-twin-universe state, mock services, etc.) — never
# commit. DTU profiles under digital-twin-universe/profiles/ are checked-in
# test fixtures (not scratch), so they're explicitly re-included below.
#
# NOTE: re-including nested paths under an ignored directory requires
# ignoring each level's *contents* (`dir/*`) rather than the bare directory
# (`dir/`) -- a bare `dir/` short-circuits git's recursion into that
# directory entirely, so deeper `!` negations are never even evaluated.
# Proven with `git check-ignore -v` against all three checked-in profiles.
.amplifier/*
!.amplifier/digital-twin-universe/
.amplifier/digital-twin-universe/*
!.amplifier/digital-twin-universe/profiles/
.amplifier/digital-twin-universe/profiles/*
!.amplifier/digital-twin-universe/profiles/*.yaml
